    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is currently not in roadworthy shape. The engine suffers from significant mechanical issues, including a suspected blown head gasket and a failing alternator, while the transmission shifts harshly between gears. Externally, the car shows its age with visible rust on the wheel arches, faded clear coat, and several prominent dents on the passenger side. The interior has seen better days, with torn upholstery and non-functional power windows. This car is best suited for a buyer looking for a major restoration project or a reliable source of salvageable parts.",
